        <div class="agenda">
            <h2><strong>Agenda</strong></h2><br>
            <p>Explore various opportunities for engineering graduates to study abroad in specialized fields such as Computer Science & IT, Mechanical Engineering, Electronics & Communication Engineering, Electrical and Electronics Engineering, and Civil Engineering. Learn about the application process, scholarships, and steps to get started.</p>
